    <item>
      <title>随着企业转向人民币，中国 9 月份资本流入大幅增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/china-s-capital-inflow-jumps-in-september-as-firms-shift-to-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国降息导致美元资产回报率降低，中国企业上月纷纷将资金转回本土市场，导致月度资本流入创约两年来最大纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/china-s-capital-inflow-jumps-in-september-as-firms-shift-to-yuan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:20:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代印度首次公开募股 (IPO) 创纪录后股价首日下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/hyundai-india-shares-fall-in-debut-after-record-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车公司印度子公司的股票在孟买下跌。此前，现代汽车印度有限公司在该国有史以来规模最大的首次公开募股中筹集了 33 亿美元。朱莉娅·菲奥雷蒂在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/hyundai-india-shares-fall-in-debut-after-record-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国赤字上升给财政大臣预算出台带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/uk-records-higher-borrowing-than-expected-in-first-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国本财年上半年的政府赤字大于预期，这加大了财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的压力，迫使她提高税收并增加借款以在下周的预算中弥补更高的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/uk-records-higher-borrowing-than-expected-in-first-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北美交易时段日元抛售势将加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/yen-selling-set-to-intensify-during-north-american-trading-hours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻分析显示，当北美交易员上线时，日元兑美元的抛售往往会加剧，这表明日元最大的卖空交易来自何处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/yen-selling-set-to-intensify-during-north-american-trading-hours</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:07:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新考虑美联储路径，债券普遍遭遇抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bonds-are-selling-off-everywhere-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者考虑美国降息步伐放缓的前景，全球债券价格正在下跌，这一趋势有可能颠覆各地的债务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bonds-are-selling-off-everywhere-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 02:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车印度公司首次公开募股 (IPO) 后股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/hyundai-motor-india-set-to-debut-after-nation-s-largest-ever-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现代汽车印度有限公司 (Hyundai Motor India Ltd.) 股价周二在孟买上市首日下跌近 6%，由于散户投资者反应不佳，作为印度有史以来最大规模的首次公开募股 (IPO)，其开盘表现不温不火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/hyundai-motor-india-set-to-debut-after-nation-s-largest-ever-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 01:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私人信贷管理公司 Monroe 将多数股权出售给 Wendel</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/private-credit-manager-monroe-sells-majority-stake-to-wendel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于巴黎的 Wendel 已同意以 11.3 亿美元收购私人贷款机构 Monroe Capital 的多数股权，这家公司正将其业务范围拓展到蓬勃发展的私人信贷领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/private-credit-manager-monroe-sells-majority-stake-to-wendel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 00:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商继续关注中东局势，油价在飙升后下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于整体金融市场呈现避险基调，且交易员继续关注中东地区以色列和伊朗之间的紧张局势，油价在周一上涨近 2% 后有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
